UID:tOhAUMk-R6cwmaGV6zFr4
SUMMARY:LANDSCAPE TECHNICIAN BOOTCAMP
DTSTAMP:20260327T033915Z
DTSTART:20260403T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:LANDSCAPE TECHNICIAN BOOTCAMP Friday\, April 3\, 2026 Lake Wash
	ington Institute of Technology – 11605 132nd Avenue NE\, Kirkland\, WA 980
	34-8506 TITLE SPONSOR - DURANTA The Washington Association of Landscape Pr
	ofessionals is excited to offer the LANDSCAPE TECHNICIAN BOOTCAMP training
	 in partnership with the National Association of Landscape Professionals. 
	WALP will be offering the LANDSCAPE TECHNICIAN BOOTCAMP in APRIL 3\, 2026 
	at Lake Washington Insitute of Technology that will be comprehensive train
	ing for your staff and workforce. Hands-On Training For Your Crews! The ne
	w Landscape Technician Boot Camp will provide hands-on training for your c
	rews. Based on the curriculum for the Landscape Industry Certified Technic
	ian Exterior exam\, this industry-vetted training will help prepare your c
	rews to work more effectively in 2026.  Boot Camp includes training in tec
	hniques and safety in 15 different competency areas organized into 3 disci
	plines presented in Spanish and English! Bonus! This course also helps pre
	pare people for the Landscape Industry Certified Technician Exterior exam.
	 So\, once you’ve trained your team\, consider registering them to become 
	certified through the National Association of Landscape Professionals \\(N
	ALP\\). Registration Costs: WALP Members \\(First 5 registrants\\): $95.00
	 per person WALP Members \\(6\\+ registrants\\): $80.00 per person NON-WAL
	P Members : $145.00 per person\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/de
	tails/landscape-technician-bootcamp/18291064/2026-04-03T00\n\nFrom SEAtoda
	y - Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/landscape-technician-boot
	camp/18291064/2026-04-03T00
LOCATION:Lake Washington Institute of Technology - LWTech\, 11605 132nd Ave
	 NE\, Kirkland\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT10H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:HAyl3CRvTEPr2X-uxi4tU
SUMMARY:March Madness Watch Party at Five Iron Golf - Seattle Capitol Hill
DTSTAMP:20260327T033915Z
DTSTART:20260403T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Five Iron Golf is your College Basketball HQ this March! Gather
	 your crew and book 1–2 simulator bays for up to 12 people \\(6 people per
	 bay\\) for a bracket-busting watch party experience. Enjoy all-day TV cov
	erage of college basketball alongside cutting-edge golf and multisport sim
	ulators\, a locally-inspired menu\, and custom beverage packages.\n\nBook 
	your watch party for March 19 or 20 and you'll automatically be entered to
	 win a 20-person happy hour with drinks and appetizers — a $1\,000 value!\
	n\nGroup packages can include reserved event space\, team-specific décor\,
	 a dedicated staff member\, full-screen and/or picture-in-picture viewing\
	, a customizable menu\, beverage packages\, free club rentals\, multisport
	 simulators\, and table games. Select the "Small Event" option at booking 
	to ensure simulator bays are placed side-by-side. Availability of select f
	eatures varies by location.\n\nPromotions:\n\nHappy Hour – "It's 5i o'Cloc
	k Somewhere" \\(Monday–Friday\, 3–6 PM\\)\n\nEnjoy $5 bottomless boneless 
	wings\, $10 bottomless bone-in wings\, $5 select beers/cans/cocktails\, $5
	 dips \\(guacamole\, hot honey ricotta\, hummus\\)\, half-off pizzas\, and
	 $5 featured shots. Dine-in only at participating locations\; simulator re
	ntal may be required.\n\n5i After Dark – "Swing In\, For Less"  \\(Sunday–
	Thursday 9 PM to close | Friday–Saturday 10 PM to close\\)\n\nFeatures $29
	/hr simulator rentals plus the same great food and drink specials as Happy
	 Hour\, with wings priced per dozen rather than bottomless. Dine-in only a
	t participating locations\; simulator rental may be required.\n\nhttps://s
	eatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/march-madness-watch-party-at-five-iro
	n-golf-seattle-capitol-hill/18268907/2026-04-03T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Spor
	ts & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/march-madness-watch-party
	-at-five-iron-golf-seattle-capitol-hill/18268907/2026-04-03T00
LOCATION:Five Iron Golf - Seattle Capitol Hill\, 1525 11th Ave Suite 100\, 
	Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT12H
END:VEVENT
